<p>
  <span class="nym">Airard</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>heri</i> 'host, army' + <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>hard</i>, <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>hart</i> 'strong, hard'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


